com.keevosh.springframework.boot.netbeans

Class SpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.keevosh.springframework.boot.netbeans.SpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.netbeans.spi.editor.completion.CompletionProvider

    public class SpringBootConfigurationCompletionProvider
extends Object
implements org.netbeans.spi.editor.completion.CompletionProvider
    The Spring Boot Configuration implementation of CompletionProvider. The entry point of completion support. This provider is registered for text/x-properties files and is enabled if spring-boot is available on the classpath. It scans the classpath for META-INF/spring-configuration-metadata.json files, Then demarshalls the files into the corresponding ConfigurationMetadata classes and later in the query task scans for items and fills the CompletionResultSet.
    Author:
    Aggelos Karalias
